Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me all about Nana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear about your feelings for her, and once I sort out my feelings about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think I might be able to keep going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:48.77,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:54.74,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:01:00.87,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:06.83,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:14.22,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:18.93,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:24.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:33.73,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:38.66,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:45.79,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:52.55,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:48.77,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:54.74,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:01:00.87,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:06.83,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:14.22,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:18.93,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:24.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:33.73,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:38.66,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:45.79,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:52.55,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:06.68,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,960)\pos(160,381)\fscx112.5\fscy103.75}Episode 17 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... class isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... there's a student council meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was declined!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come with me for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided whether I want to go out with you again just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I think you already know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, which is better for you? Saturday or Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... let's meet in front of the station at {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}11 {\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}AM on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a date or anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he looks so happy like that, my feelings get mixed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can really see the shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...written all over his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you already know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this isn't a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought she'd be all yours again if you went with her today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:43.28,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx196.25\fscy271.25\b1\c&HB06851&\frz3.582\move(294,288,306,288,0,855)}Bullseye
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, this may have made things a little more strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to tell me all about Nana-san, but now I wonder if this will really work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what there is to say... I met her in my second year of middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she accidentally died during the summer of my third year. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what more can you determine from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that... I don't really know how to respond...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Takahashi and Nana-san were swept out to sea and were drowning, who would you save first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could only put it simply like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get something to eat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... this place has a buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm trying to affirm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a slice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yano's feelings for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you still have the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yano, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yano...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, do you have the picture Yano was using for his background?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one of you in the yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent it to you before, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it, and do it well, I'll give you this as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me you erased it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you over and over, but you kept telling me you didn't have it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, why'd you delete your background?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:57.41,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: The following scene is a series of very Japanese puns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, Gouda Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hook-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're eating right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hook-up party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely Complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.01,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Love Com, another shoujo manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a hook-up party, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A general contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so you went to a hook-up party...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.34,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: An actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sankhon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, umm, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me explain! Umm, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd wait for me, and you went to a hook-party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I kinda got caught in the flow, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-July?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty soon afterwards, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... they forced me to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to find a new girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... I wouldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only girl I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be pulled back in by Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna leave for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he'll say anything else about Nana-san today, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two try having a normal date now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the condition of him telling you about Nana-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that was just a trigger for you to forgive him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try becoming a little more honest with your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everything will just get messed up again if I start going with my emotions, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi... are you sure it's not Moto but you who's obsessed with Nana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't bring yourself to believe in him, what's meant to be won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd Take go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you wouldn't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think we met today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anywhere else you want to go today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink! Drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just juice, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so depressed, Take-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't be such a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're throwing a consolation party!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We always think of our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I say something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've... I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been confessed to by two different girls this school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go out with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I go with them if I don't feel anything towards them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try going out and feel something for them later?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could do that... I'd force my way and steal her from him... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the root of things, those two have mutual love for each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:18.62,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\bord2\fscx346.25\fscy326.25\b1\c&HA7E1EF&\3c&H6C7AD0&\pos(325,66)}Mutual Love
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mutual love... sure sounds nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Li'l Mi. What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he was annoying me, I teased him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During last year's summer festival, she was desperately looking for Moto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much that she was out of breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, she wouldn't have to find me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I'd always find her first, like I do now.
