Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I really don't need this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are his allies, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no good unless he has a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type of guy who's no good unless he has a girl to support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the type who always needs someone to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone to protect? What's up with that? Sounds like it'd be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be so much easier without something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree, but people always shine the brightest when they have someone to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know if he's realized it himself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he doesn't trust women at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's probably what's making things so difficult for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Was it during the first year of middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when his mother got remarried?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was her first marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think his mom sees his current dad as her first husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a normal date now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I get changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll be right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I came all the way out to his house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You got a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What breed is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just a mutt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the one that was abandoned in front of Take's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that seriously the same puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puppies grow, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm such a moron. That dog made me so soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala? That's a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you'd be a really caring dad, unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just get that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you haven't really seemed that family-oriented, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to have a warm household with three kids, a big dog, and a basketball net in my driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three kids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer just one, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you only had one, the kid wouldn't have anyone to play with, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try a little harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe two at most, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One girl and one boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good, either! You have to have two boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm going to marry you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was kinda mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had two boys, they could still play catch with each other even when dad's at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done anything with my dad before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only memories I have of my dad are from what my mom's told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said he died soon after I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died young from disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time Yano's told me about his dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he was athletic and a swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During his school years, he got his name on some plaque at a Hokkaido event.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's told me so many times, I've been able to form an image of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though I've never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fourth grade, I asked my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you have a picture of Dad?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Show me what Dad looks like."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, your dad's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like him when he was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the splitting image of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cheerful, a prankster, smart and handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Year after year, it's shocking how much you're becoming like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he and I are like two peas in a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like two peas in a pod?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see! I would've loved to have seen that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your face will look like your dad's when you grow up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Was there a picture? How'd he look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't really tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go fetch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it back to me. Good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... her collar has her name and Yano's telephone number on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:16.01,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fscx167.5\fscy182.5\frx18\fry358\pos(324,209)\frz356.961}Lalami
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala... mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much more we can do today anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me walk you to the bus stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he says any more... I feel like I'll give in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we... hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that means... we can't kiss, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.07,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H878697&\fscx326.25\fscy310\pos(446,206)\frz26.531}Bus
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A goodbye handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably... being a terrible tease to Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodging his actions and being mean... as if I were taunting him with a bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough strength to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's words keep coming and going...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and there's no reason to hesitate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but my will and what I feel in my heart are two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do know my own feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But belief in him... needs the strength of my will to support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...contradicting myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Motoharu, your timing's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you carry that flowerpot over here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one. The Felicite Parmentier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fe... Feli?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one that had white flowers over the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to the Constance Spry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Con?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roses over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you make this arch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it look nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come spring, it'll be covered in pink flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it dreamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Makes you almost impatient for it to come, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're having a hard time talking with me again, like long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you always talked so much, and you'd tell me everything that happened to you that day when you come home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really... it's just that I've become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's a swimmer, and he got first place all the time in high school competitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm gonna be a swimmer, just like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy you're his bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a "bastard"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a kind of sausage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Yano-kun's fighting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't seem to get the time down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.64,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}Sign: Swimming Preliminary Matches
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... why do you always stare into the mirror before a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some kind of superstition or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It helps me concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sad. You gave it all you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you got second place. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you disappointed in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my son, so I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu. Let's go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... we're probably gonna see someone, like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The husband of one of Mom's best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like a skeleton... it makes me sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just look at him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since... he's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he the husband of one of your friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... am I Mrs. Michiko's son...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Motoharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found someone I want to marry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you really need a father figure at your age, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do the things I really want always pass right before my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I want them to be there, they always leave me...
