Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:51.05,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&HFFFFFF&\fscx128.75\fscy130\pos(215,337)\frx12\fry354\frz21.472}Takahashi, next time I'll\Nproperly talk about Nana-san,\NSo, please meet with me\Nagain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if I don't want that... it keeps happening anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hopes are never fulfilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my good luck never lasts for very long...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life never goes the way I want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.99,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx187.5\fscy202.5\frz350.613\pos(511,216)\c&HFAFCFD&}Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.99,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx163.75\fscy207.5\pos(403,358)\frz350.396\c&HFEFFF9&}Okay. -Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if my good luck is to turn into bad luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't my bad luck change into good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing that, I continue to live on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:08.80,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima kimi ga iikaketa kotoba ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:15.27,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yubisaki ni sotto oritekita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:21.90,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo iwanakute ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:27.70,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumaida yubi wo gyutto atatamete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:44.21,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba wa kotoba dakara kokoro hanbun mo tsutaenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:57.39,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute yuuyake futari wo tsutsundeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:10.11,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Komiageru mune no omoi kokoro ga itai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:21.13,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshi kimi ga tabibito ni nattara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:27.84,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kore gurai kimi wo matteru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:33.89,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu wa kawaru sono tabi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:40.10,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kioku ga usuragu koto ga attemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:56.37,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka wo konna fuu ni kokoro ippai de aisenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:24:03.67,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaritai taisetsu na kimi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:09.59,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsu datte futari wa hitori ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:17.27,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mune ga kawaresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:23.06,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Furete hoshii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.52,0:24:39.33,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute kaerenai kono mama aruiteitai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.33,0:24:54.64,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yabaisaki ni kanjiteiru kokoro no kotoba wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:08.80,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The words you were just about to say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:15.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,fell softly onto my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:21.90,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:27.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clasp your hand tightly and warm it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:44.21,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Because words are words, I can't express half of the feelings in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:57.39,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating as the sunset engulfs the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:10.11,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches from all the feelings welling up inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:21.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to become a traveler,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:27.84,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,would I be able to wait for you as I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:33.89,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As the seasons change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:40.10,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even if our memories are to fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:56.37,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to love someone with all of my heart like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:24:03.67,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect the precious you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:09.59,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:17.27,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart feels so fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:23.06,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.52,0:24:39.33,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating that I can't go home. I want to keep walking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.33,0:24:54.64,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the words from your heart on my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.95,0:25:34.97,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\fscx97.5\fscy123.75\pos(430,377)}Episode 18 Preview ...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.73,0:25:10.03,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think Nana-san\N loved you a whole lot, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.03,0:25:12.49,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's\N regretting it even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.49,0:25:15.53,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she's\N regretting leaving you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.53,0:25:19.12,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,She could just die\N for making you so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:22.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure, even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:25.79,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...from heaven,\N she's watching over you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.79,0:25:31.30,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...\N I can't make you happy.
